---
const homeUrl = '/'
const docsCenterUrl = '/docs-center/'
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
        <title>HUAT FSAC</title>
        <meta name="robots" content="noindex,follow" />
        <meta http-equiv="refresh" content={`1;url=${homeUrl}`} />
        <style>
            :root {
                color-scheme: light dark;
            }

            body {
                margin: 0;
                min-height: 100vh;
                display: grid;
                place-items: center;
                font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
                background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #20242d 0%, #0f1115 68%);
                color: #f5f7fb;
            }

            main {
                width: min(32rem, calc(100% - 2rem));
                padding: 2rem;
                border-radius: 1rem;
                background: rgba(15, 17, 21, 0.82);
                border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
                box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
            }

            h1 {
                margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }

            p {
                margin: 0 0 1rem;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: rgba(245, 247, 251, 0.82);
            }

            .actions {
                display: flex;
                gap: 0.75rem;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
            }

            a {
                color: inherit;
                text-decoration: none;
                padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
                border-radius: 999px;
                border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            }

            a.primary {
                background: #f39c12;
                border-color: #f39c12;
                color: #151515;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <main>
            <h1>站点入口已更新</h1>
            <p>`/docs/` 现在作为旧入口保留。页面将自动跳转到首页，你也可以直接打开文档中心。</p>
            <div class="actions">
                <a class="primary" href={homeUrl}>前往首页</a>
                <a href={docsCenterUrl}>打开文档中心</a>
            </div>
        </main>
        <script>
            window.setTimeout(() => {
                window.location.replace('/');
            }, 1000);
        </script>
    </body>
</html>
